# 🔹 EMPLOYEE FUNCTIONALITIES

## What Employee Can Do

### 1️⃣ Login

* Logs in using RBAC
* Role = EMPLOYEE

### 2️⃣ View Payslip Page

Route:

```
/employee/payslips
```

Backend filters:

```
WHERE employee_id = loggedInUser.id
```

Employee sees:

* Month
* Gross Salary
* Net Salary
* Status
* Download PDF

❌ Cannot:

* View others
* Edit anything
* Regenerate

Security Rule:

```
if (user.role !== "EMPLOYEE") reject
if (payslip.employee_id !== user.id) reject
```

---

# 🔹 MANAGER FUNCTIONALITIES (View-Only Control)

Managers can:

### 1️⃣ View Payroll Flow Dashboard

Route:

```
/manager/payroll-overview
```

They can see:

* Payroll batch status
* Team salary summary
* Total payroll expense
* Approval stage

But:

❌ No Generate button
❌ No Approve button
❌ No Edit option

Backend restriction:

```
if (user.role === "MANAGER") {
   allow GET requests only
   block POST / PUT / DELETE
}
```

---

# 🔹 ADMIN FUNCTIONALITIES (Full Control)

Admin Dashboard:

```
/admin/payroll
```

Admin can:

### 1️⃣ Create Payroll Batch

### 2️⃣ Generate Payslips

### 3️⃣ Approve Batch

### 4️⃣ Lock Batch

### 5️⃣ Release Payslips

Before LOCK:
✔ Can regenerate
✔ Can correct values

After LOCK:
❌ No editing

After RELEASE:
❌ Fully immutable

